                    <ab><rs key="#Offersio/donatio">Donatio</rs> (ut videtur, est enim charta lacera
                        et pene deleta) <rs key="#Houses">domorum</rs>, facta a <persName><name
                                ref="Maurizo">Mauritio</name></persName> filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Gregorius Ravennatis">Gregorii
                                Ravennatis</name></persName>, favore <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Offersio/donatio #Houses #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460"><placeName ref="#places/4179"
                                >Pomposiani</placeName></orgName> et domini <persName key="#Abbots"
                            ref="#people/1574">Widonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbatis</rs>. Actum <placeName ref="#places/594"
                            >Ravennê</placeName>. Rog. … notarii. Anno <persName key="#Popes"
                            ref="#people/1591">Benedicti</persName>
                        <rs key="#Popes">papê</rs> et <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/261">Conradi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperatoris</rs>, indictione … .</ab>
